
Pytest HTML Reports
Info_website - https://pypl.org/project/pytest-html/

How to create html reports with pytest

install module = pip install pytest-html

- Run test by pytest --html=<filename>.html here file name
is to the name given to the HTML report generated
- Run single test and generate report
    pytest <test_name>.py --html=<filename>.html
- Navigate to save reports in folder specified
    --html=./reports/report1.html --self-contained-html
    this will generate a new folder and create reports in it
    without --self-contained-html test will generate Assets folder with Css file

